# NeuroCluster Website - Complete Project Structure

## 📁 Project Overview

**NeuroCluster_website/** - Academic showcase website for the NeuroCluster Streamer (NCS) algorithm, featuring interactive demonstrations, comprehensive documentation, and a research blog.

## 🌳 Folder Structure

```
NeuroCluster_website/
├── 📄 index.html                      # Main landing page with hero section
├── 📄 README.md                       # Project documentation
├── 📄 package.json                    # Node.js dependencies (if needed)
├── 📄 .gitignore                      # Git ignore rules
│
├── 📁 assets/                         # Static assets
│   ├── 📁 css/                       # Stylesheets
│   │   ├── 📄 main.css               # Primary styles
│   │   ├── 📄 components.css         # Component-specific styles
│   │   ├── 📄 academic.css           # Academic styling theme
│   │   ├── 📄 demo.css               # Interactive demo styles
│   │   ├── 📄 blog.css               # Blog-specific styles
│   │   └── 📄 responsive.css         # Mobile responsiveness
│   │
│   ├── 📁 js/                        # JavaScript files
│   │   ├── 📄 main.js                # Core functionality
│   │   ├── 📄 ncs-simulator.js       # Algorithm simulation
